00:00:20.287 --> 00:00:21.622 align:middle line:90%
Welcome to "Gaiam Inspirations."

00:00:21.622 --> 00:00:24.524 align:middle line:84%
We're coming to you live
from Boulder, Colorado,

00:00:24.524 --> 00:00:26.526 align:middle line:84%
here at the Gaiam
Studios in Boulder.

00:00:26.526 --> 00:00:28.729 align:middle line:84%
And we encourage you
to interact with us

00:00:28.729 --> 00:00:30.163 align:middle line:90%
via Facebook and Twitter.

00:00:30.163 --> 00:00:32.499 align:middle line:84%
